title: BBC Documentary: Edwardians in colour
description:
A five part BBC series about the Alberth Kahn collection of early colour photographs.

This series cover the time around World War I.


This is my second Torrent, so please bear with any problems.

I do not have unlimited upload speed, so you need to be a bit patient. However, I will keep seeding day and night until there are enough seeders.


My last upload "The twenties in colour" took a week of seeding, so we are looking at something like that here too, just keep leeching.
